<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; color: #222; }

    /* Página de instrucciones (portada) */
    .cover { padding: 10px 6px; page-break-after: always; }
    .cover h1 { color: #c0392b; font-size: 26px; margin: 0 0 4px; }
    .cover .sub { color: #555; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
    .steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; counter-reset: step; }
    .steps li {
      position: relative; padding: 12px 14px 12px 52px; margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .steps li::before {
      counter-increment: step; content: counter(step);
      position: absolute; left: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background: #c0392b; color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold; text-align: center; line-height: 28px;
    }
    .wa-box {
      margin-top: 22px; padding: 14px 16px; border: 2px dashed #25D366; border-radius: 12px;
      background: #f3fff7; text-align: center;
    }
    .wa-box .num { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #128C7E; letter-spacing: 1px; }

    /* Parrilla de productos: 2 columnas */
    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; padding: 4px 2px; }
    .card {
      border: 1px solid #d9d9d9; border-radius: 10px; padding: 8px; position: relative;
      break-inside: avoid; text-align: center; background: #fff;
    }
    .card .code {
      position: absolute; top: 6px; left: 6px; font-weight: bold; color: #c0392b;
      font-size: 20px; background: #fff; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .card .badges { position: absolute; top: 6px; right: 6px; text-align: right; }
    .card .badge {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; padding: 4px 9px;
      border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 4px; border: 1px solid #00000022;
    }
    .badge-new { background: #fff3cd; color: #856404; }
    .badge-unique { background: #f8d7da; color: #842029; }
    .card .photo {
      width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: contain; margin: 18px 0 6px;
    }
    .card .photo-missing {
      width: 100%; height: 180px; margin: 18px 0 6px; display: flex;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #bbb; font-size: 12px;
      background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .card .name { font-size: 11px; color: #333; min-height: 28px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .card .price { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #111; margin-top: 4px; }
    .card .brand { font-size: 9px; color: #999; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="cover">
    <% if logo.present? %>
      <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="Pasatiempos" style="height:90px; margin-bottom:10px;">
    <% end %>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <p class="sub">Pasatiempos — Coleccionables</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:16px;color:#333;">¿Cómo ordenar?</h2>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>Anota los <strong>códigos</strong> de las piezas que te interesen.</li>
      <li>Mándalos por WhatsApp al número de abajo.</li>
      <li>Pide el <strong>total incluyendo el envío</strong>.</li>
      <li>Deposita y envía los datos de a dónde se enviará el paquete.</li>
      <li>¡Recibe el paquete y disfruta tus piezas!</li>
    </ol>
    <div class="wa-box">
      <div>Pide por WhatsApp</div>
      <div class="num"><%= whatsapp_number %></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <% items.each do |item| %>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="code"><%= item[:code] %></span>
        <% if item[:badges].present? %>
          <span class="badges">
            <% item[:badges].each do |b| %>
              <span class="badge <%= b == 'Nuevo' ? 'badge-new' : 'badge-unique' %>"><%= b %></span><br>
            <% end %>
          </span>
        <% end %>
        <% if item[:image].present? %>
          <img class="photo" src="<%= item[:image] %>" alt="">
        <% else %>
          <div class="photo-missing">Sin imagen</div>
        <% end %>
        <div class="name"><%= truncate(item[:name].to_s, length: 60) %></div>
        <% if item[:brand].present? %><div class="brand"><%= item[:brand] %></div><% end %>
        <div class="price"><%= number_to_currency(item[:price], unit: "$", precision: 0) %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
